This product contains lactic acid, mandelic acid, and vitamin C—ingredients known to work deep within the skin to target pigmentation and tanning. With consistent use for four weeks, it can help reduce dark spots and leave your skin looking more even-toned and clear. It’s important to apply it every single day without skipping, as consistency is key to seeing visible results. While you can use it at night, if you’re applying it in the morning, make sure to follow up with a body lotion that contains SPF 50 for proper sun protection. The formulation is lightweight and gentle, making it suitable for most skin types without causing irritation. For best results, I prefer rubbing it in slightly after application and letting it dry down a bit—this helps the product absorb better and work more effectively.
